gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係岩岩好睇到哩段,咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cc764ab0617d5af5752f917eb451bb68183abe","tid":418014,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"嘩屌第四章開頭咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f66957c1b0640bc3d7a3b781ac9a7288ca38f6f","tid":418014,"uid":40078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>百田吐血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係岩岩好睇到哩段,咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咗春川一拳都無理由搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c5aa8f662fc0f1bdff0a69c56d908a223c3659","tid":418014,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"跳驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac09784e779514c6a85aec657651cbab567a541","tid":418014,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"呢章唔洗審已經知邊個係兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5955b79aec6f751f58c29d571b54bde6553b16","tid":418014,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢卜十"},{"pid":"84f2d8eaae517531fd00254b61323d1499367f31","tid":418014,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"有幾個位唔係好明<br />\n殺轉子把鐮刀點蚊返出黎？如果事後開白布拎 先唔講要有幾大動作 地板咁明顯會冇人留意到？<br />\n<br />\n密室環境點確認把日本刀冇卡住係門鎖 即使成功鎖門 卡住既情況只要見到就立即破解密室"},{"pid":"805433c199457bb108ef3466ccb2651b09f827e2","tid":418014,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾個位唔係好明<br />\n殺轉子把鐮刀點蚊返出黎？如果事後開白布拎 先唔講要有幾大動作 地板咁明顯會冇人留意到？<br />\n<br />\n密室環境點確認把日本刀冇卡住係門鎖 即使成功鎖門 卡住既情況只要見到就立即破解密室</blockquote><br />\n1. 鐮刀攝係鐵籠隙度，佢收白布事先用手隔住塊布捉實把鐮刀先咪得<br />\n<br />\n2. 雖然唔太明你句地板咁明顯係指咩，但果間房就算有蠟燭都係好暗(無機望連搜證都做唔到)，有啲咩留意唔到都唔奇<br />\n<br />\n3. 咁佢係出面試下開唔開到後門個鎖咪得，反正夜晚大把時間可以慢慢試到鎖得到果下<br />\n<br />\n至於卡住我都覺係問題，不過大概真宮寺就係為左出現哩個問題都無咁顯眼先吊起埋另外3個蠟像或多或少掩飾下"},{"pid":"44426642eca7bebc8df1990702301572e607f113","tid":418014,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢章唔洗審已經知邊個係兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兇手唔算太難估嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過哩章最難其實係個手法，我覺得咁樣用蹺蹺板真係異想天開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}